ORIX is Built on a Strong FoundationORIX’s established financial stability and access to deep resources empowers our teams to design and implement the kind of flexible, forward-thinking capital solutions other companies can’t. 



Publicly Traded
ORIX USA is the U.S. subsidiary of ORIX Corporation, a publicly owned Tokyo-based international financial services company founded in 1964.  ORIX Corporation is listed on the Tokyo (8591) and New York (NYSE:IX) Stock Exchanges.



Global Reach, Capital Ready
Operating in 36 countries and regions worldwide, our parent company, ORIX Corporation, is a diversified financial conglomerate with more than $90 billion in assets and more than $300 billion of assets under management.    



Investment Grade
Leading bond rating companies recognize our financial strength, awarding ORIX Corporation investment grade credit ratings.

