Our Business
Founded in 1981 as the U.S. subsidiary of ORIX Corporation, ORIX USA has transformed into a diversified financial company with the ability to provide investment capital and asset management services to clients in the corporate, real estate and municipal finance sectors.


A Diverse and Dynamic Offering
With businesses spanning corporate lending, private equity, venture finance, commercial real estate, municipal finance and healthcare, ORIX serves as a growth catalyst for business.  Always adapting to meet the specific needs of our clients, we offer a continually expanding set of customized products and services including, but certainly not limited to:

Middle-Market Lending, Mezzanine and Private Equity
Venture Capital
Commercial Real Estate Bridge and Construction Capital
Multifamily and Senior Living Bridge and Agency Capital
Municipal and Infrastructure Finance
Fund Investments and Alternative Strategies
Structured Products
Energy Debt and Equity Solutions
Healthcare Debt and Equity Solutions
Asset Management
Large Strategic Investments and Partnerships





























